data.description: Come and explore this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, nestled in the vibrant heart of Saint Petersburg. This home has been freshly upgraded in 2023. Features include refinished hardwood and new vinyl-plank flooring, refinished bathroom with walk-in shower. New Samsung stainless-steel appliances- including large capacity Wifi refrigerator and induction-top stove with built-in air fryer and convection oven, and new three rack large-capacity stainless steel Kitchen Aid dishwasher. Roof and HVAC installed in 2016.  Its prime location offers proximity to shopping, schools, transportation, and entertainment.  It is located .2 miles from Twin Brooks Golf Course, .3 miles from the Skyway Trail, .6 miles from Clam Bayou Nature Park, 2.5 miles from Maximo Park, 1.7 miles from Gulfport Beach, and 1.5 miles from the up-and-coming Skyway Marina district.  It is an ideal choice for both homeowners and savvy investors. In today's competitive market, homes of this caliber, especially those move-in ready like this one, are a rare find. Act quickly, or you might miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
